'''羅伯特·吉布斯'''（Robert Gibbs；{{bd|1971年|3月29日}}）是[[麥當勞|麥當勞]]公司的副總裁和麥當勞的公關負責人<ref>{{cite news|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|title=McDonald's hires former White House press secretary Robert Gibbs|url=http://money.cnn.com/2015/06/09/news/companies/mcdonalds-gibbs-white-house-press-secretary/index.html|first=Aaron|last=Smith|date=9 June 2015|accessdate=10 June 2015|archive-date=2019-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190428181032/https://money.cnn.com/2015/06/09/news/companies/mcdonalds-gibbs-white-house-press-secretary/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在加入麥當勞之前，吉布斯曾經在奧巴馬的第一個任期內擔任[[白宮發言人|白宮發言人]]<ref name=midname>{{cite news|publisher=WRAL.com|title=N.C. State grad tapped as Obama's press secretary|url=http://www.wral.com/news/political/story/4011601/|first=Joan|last=Lowy|date=22 November 2008|accessdate=March 13, 2010|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303190739/http://www.wral.com/news/political/story/4011601/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2012年，吉布斯曾經擔任歐巴馬的高級競選顧問。

